    "text": "### FILE: OEBPS/author.html\n\nThe Rites of Hajj, Practical Treatise and Rules\n\nAuthor(s):\nNaser Makarem Shirazi [3]\n\n### FILE: OEBPS/translator.html\n\nThe Rites of Hajj, Practical Treatise and Rules\n\nTranslator(s):\nBahador Shirazian [4]\n\n### FILE: OEBPS/category.html\n\nThe Rites of Hajj, Practical Treatise and Rules\n\nCategory:\nHajj (Hija) [5]\n\n### FILE: OEBPS/featured_category.html\n\nThe Rites of Hajj, Practical Treatise and Rules\n\nFeatured Category:\nDesturi za Waislamu [6]\n\n### FILE: OEBPS/footer.html\n\nThe Rites of Hajj, Practical Treatise and Rules\n\nSource URL: https://www.al-islam.org/sw/rites-hajj-practical-treatise-and-rules-naser-makarem-shirazi\n\nLinks\n[1] https://www.al-islam.org/sw/user/login?destination=node/30490%23comment-form\n[2] https://www.al-islam.org/sw/user/register?destination=node/30490%23comment-form\n[3] https://www.al-islam.org/sw/person/naser-makarem-shirazi\n[4] https://www.al-islam.org/sw/person/bahador-shirazian"
