    "ref": "### FILE: OEBPS/epub.html",
    "heading": "### FILE: OEBPS/epub.html",
    "text": "We ask Allah, Glorified be He, for guidance and success in acting in accordance with it.\n\nThe Rules of Taqleed and Tahaarah"
