    "heading": "The conditions (in the correctness) of Wudhu’ are twelve:",
    "text": "Issue 131: The conditions (in the correctness) of Wudhu’ are twelve:\nFirst, the purity [or Tahaarah] of the water of Wudhu’.\nSecond, that the water is pure [Mutlaq] water. Based on this, the Wudhu’ performed with Mutanajjis water or Mixed [Mudhaaf] water is invalid, although the person making Wudhu’ doesn't know of that or he forgot. If he prays with that Wudhu’, it is obligatory to repeat the prayer."
