    "text": "Issue 84: Fifth , it is obligatory that the body of the worshipper, his clothing and the place of his prostration be pure. The explanation of these matters will also come in the examination of the clothing of the worshipper and his place (of worship).\nPurifiers (Mutahhiraat)\nWater\nPhysical Change (Istihaalah)"
