    "heading": "The eating of something filthy by which man's nature is repulsed, is forbidden (like mucus and similar things) although it is pure.",
    "text": "Issue 925: The eating of something filthy by which man's nature is repulsed, is forbidden (like mucus and similar things) although it is pure."
