    "id": "makarem-summary-949",
    "sourceId": "makarem-summary",
    "source": "A Summary of Rulings",
    "ref": "Issue 934",
    "heading": "The vow is only proper when a Seeghah is executed for it whether it be in 'Arabic, Persian or any other language.",
    "text": "Issue 934: The vow is only proper when a Seeghah is executed for it whether it be in 'Arabic, Persian or any other language."
